---

<main class="page">
  <h1>Getting Started</h1>
  <p>Open LottieDa, draw a shape, edit its properties, and save the document as `animation.json`.</p>

  <h2>Keyboard Shortcuts</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>V: Select</li>
    <li>R: Rectangle</li>
    <li>O: Ellipse</li>
    <li>P: Path</li>
    <li>Space: Play or pause</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Builder API</h2>
  <p>The TypeScript builder in `src/engine/builder.ts` can construct v0.1 shape-layer Lottie files programmatically.</p>
</main>
